    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1905-07-11T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1905-07-11T00:00:00-05:00" n="901"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d901">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Ambassador <persName type="from">Meyer</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">St. Petersburg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-07-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 11, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>* * * Russia’s plenipotentiary and delegates will sail on <hi rend="italic"
                        >Kaiser Wilhelm</hi> due New York August 9. Mouravieff arrived here Sunday
                    morning for instructions, taken ill yesterday, causing Russian minister for
                    foreign affairs some concern, as plenipotentiary has just come from a cure at
                    Contrexeville.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Meyer.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
